## 10. L3 — API Contract（staging HTTP）

### 守护目标
端云数据合约不漂移：cursor 分页语义、错误码格式、字段可见性、响应时间 SLO

### 驱动文件
`e2e.yaml[test_type: api_contract]` — 无 UI driver，Dart HTTP client + DTO fromMap 断言

### 文件结构（强制）

```
test/cloud/content/
└── api_contract_runner.dart     # 所有 api_contract 场景合并在一个文件
```

### 覆盖三维度（强制）

每个场景必须覆盖：

| 维度 | 内容 |
|------|------|
| **协议层** | HTTP 状态码、Content-Type header |
| **结构层** | 响应 JSON 字段完整性、DTO fromMap 可解析 |
| **语义层** | computed getter 正确（aspectRatio等）、错误码枚举映射、isRetryable |

### 代码规范

```dart
// test/cloud/content/api_contract_runner.dart
import 'dart:convert';
import 'package:flutter_test/flutter_test.dart';
import 'package:http/http.dart' as http;
import 'package:quwoquan_app/cloud/runtime/cloud_runtime_config.dart';
import 'package:quwoquan_app/cloud/runtime/cloud_request_headers.dart';
import 'package:quwoquan_app/cloud/runtime/generated/content/post_base_dto.dart';
import 'package:quwoquan_app/cloud/runtime/error_codes.dart';

const _stagingBase = String.fromEnvironment('STAGING_BASE_URL');
const _testToken  = String.fromEnvironment('TEST_AUTH_TOKEN');

void main() {
  late http.Client client;
  late String seededPostId;

  setUpAll(() async {
    // 探测 staging 可达性，不可达则 skip 全部场景
    try {
      final probe = await http.head(Uri.parse(_stagingBase))
          .timeout(const Duration(seconds: 5));
      if (probe.statusCode >= 500) throw Exception('staging unavailable');
    } catch (_) {
      markTestSkipped('L3: staging unreachable, all api_contract tests skipped');
      return;
    }
    client = http.Client();
    seededPostId = await _seedPhotoPost(client);  // POST /v1/content/posts
  });

  tearDownAll(() async {
    await _deletePost(client, seededPostId);
    client.close();
  });

  // ── 场景：feed_cursor_pagination_end_to_end ───────────────────────────────
  test('feed_cursor_pagination_end_to_end', () async {
    final url = Uri.parse('$_stagingBase/v1/content/feed?type=image&limit=5');
    final sw = Stopwatch()..start();
    final resp = await client.get(url,
        headers: CloudRequestHeaders.forPage('content.feed')
          ..['Authorization'] = 'Bearer $_testToken');
    sw.stop();

    expect(resp.statusCode, 200);
    expect(sw.elapsedMilliseconds, lessThan(800), reason: 'feed API SLO <800ms');

    final body = jsonDecode(resp.body) as Map<String, dynamic>;
    final items = (body['items'] as List)
        .map((e) => PostBaseDto.fromMap(e as Map<String, dynamic>))
        .toList();
    expect(items, isNotEmpty);
    final cursor = body['cursor'] as String?;
    expect(cursor, isNotNull, reason: 'response must include cursor for pagination');

    // 第二页：无 item 重叠
    final page2Url = Uri.parse('$_stagingBase/v1/content/feed?type=image&limit=5&cursor=$cursor');
    final resp2 = await client.get(page2Url,
        headers: CloudRequestHeaders.forPage('content.feed')
          ..['Authorization'] = 'Bearer $_testToken');
    expect(resp2.statusCode, 200);
    final items2 = (jsonDecode(resp2.body)['items'] as List)
        .map((e) => (e as Map)['_id'] as String)
        .toSet();
    final ids1 = items.map((e) => e.id).toSet();
    expect(ids1.intersection(items2), isEmpty, reason: 'no item overlap between pages');
  });

  // ── 场景：error_state_displayed_correctly ────────────────────────────────
  test('error_state_displayed_correctly', () async {
    final resp = await client.get(
        Uri.parse('$_stagingBase/v1/content/posts/nonexistent_post_id_00000'),
        headers: CloudRequestHeaders.forPage('content.post')
          ..['Authorization'] = 'Bearer $_testToken');

    expect(resp.statusCode, 404);
    final body = jsonDecode(resp.body) as Map<String, dynamic>;
    expect(body['code'], 'CONTENT.USER.post_not_found');
    expect(body['isRetryable'], false);

    // 端侧 ErrorCode 映射正确
    final code = ContentErrorCode.fromCode(body['code'] as String);
    expect(code, ContentErrorCode.postNotFound);
    expect(ContentErrorMessages.zh[code], '内容不存在或已删除');
  });
}
```

### 禁止行为

| 禁止 | 原因 |
|------|------|
| 测试依赖 staging 固定存量数据 | staging 数据轮换后测试失效 |
| 硬编码 token 或 URL | secrets 泄漏风险 |
| `Future.delayed(Duration(seconds: n))` 等待 | 用 Stopwatch + expect 代替 |
| 不做 staging 可达性探测就执行测试 | staging 不可用会误报失败 |

### 环境配置（强制）

```bash
# 本地执行
STAGING_BASE_URL=https://staging.api.quwoquan.com \
TEST_AUTH_TOKEN=<staging_test_token> \
make test-api-contract

# Makefile target（根目录）
test-api-contract:
    @if [ -z "$(STAGING_BASE_URL)" ]; then \
        echo "[L3] WARN: STAGING_BASE_URL not set, skipping"; exit 0; \
    fi
    cd quwoquan_app && flutter test test/cloud/content/api_contract_runner.dart \
        --dart-define=STAGING_BASE_URL=$(STAGING_BASE_URL) \
        --dart-define=TEST_AUTH_TOKEN=$(TEST_AUTH_TOKEN)

gate-full: gate test-api-contract
```

### CI 策略

| 触发时机 | 行为 |
|---------|------|
| daily cron（UTC 02:00） | `.github/workflows/daily-api-contract.yml`，失败通知 advisory |
| pre-release tag | release workflow 末尾调用，失败阻塞发布 |
| PR | 不触发（太慢，staging 有状态） |
| staging 不可用 | `markTestSkipped` → skip + warn，不 fail |

